484
00:34:54,175 --> 00:34:55,760
<c.ms Gothic>鉄平なら大丈夫だよ</c.ms Gothic>

485
00:34:58,304 --> 00:35:01,808
<c.ms Gothic>（静かな音楽）</c.ms Gothic>

486
00:35:01,891 --> 00:35:04,352
<c.ms Gothic>（小さなため息）</c.ms Gothic>

487
00:35:05,228 --> 00:35:06,562
<c.ms Gothic>お前は どうすんだ？</c.ms Gothic>

488
00:35:07,063 --> 00:35:09,524
<c.ms Gothic>俺は俺で 会社を興すよ</c.ms Gothic>

489
00:35:12,276 --> 00:35:13,611
<c.ms Gothic>これからはライバルだ</c.ms Gothic>

490
00:35:22,203 --> 00:35:23,329
<c.ms Gothic>鉄平</c.ms Gothic>

491
00:35:26,999 --> 00:35:28,084
<c.ms Gothic>絶対…</c.ms Gothic>

492
00:35:29,460 --> 00:35:32,088
<c.ms Gothic>21世紀を代表する会社にしろよ</c.ms Gothic>

493
00:35:37,677 --> 00:35:38,845
<c.ms Gothic>わかった</c.ms Gothic>

494
00:35:41,139 --> 00:35:43,057
<c.ms Gothic>（深く息を吸って）わかった</c.ms Gothic>

495
00:35:45,560 --> 00:35:46,769
<c.ms Gothic>俺はブレない</c.ms Gothic>

496
00:36:25,892 --> 00:36:26,893
<c.ms Gothic>（ドアをノックする音）</c.ms Gothic>

497
00:36:26,976 --> 00:36:28,019
<c.ms Gothic>（男性）失礼します</c.ms Gothic>

498
00:36:30,688 --> 00:36:33,065
<c.ms Gothic>（男性）社長</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>おもしろい話があります</c.ms Gothic>

