<c.ms Gothic>（鉄平）無理です</c.ms Gothic>

515
00:37:28,579 --> 00:37:29,664
<c.ms Gothic>社長</c.ms Gothic>

516
00:37:30,164 --> 00:37:33,000
<c.ms Gothic>すみません 取材の方が</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>お見えになっております</c.ms Gothic>

517
00:37:34,919 --> 00:37:36,254
<c.ms Gothic>あと１歩だ</c.ms Gothic>

518
00:37:38,631 --> 00:37:39,799
<c.ms Gothic>（鉄平）お待ちしておりました</c.ms Gothic>

519
00:37:44,262 --> 00:37:46,639
<c.ms Gothic>ビットラブ みんなやってるな…</c.ms Gothic>

520
00:37:51,018 --> 00:37:51,894
<c.ms Gothic>ん？</c.ms Gothic>

521
